                           <p>
                           
                           
                           
                           Folios 1-297 contain 15 quiresof 20 leaves each (1 leaf is missing after folio 11 and 1 leaf was cancelled after folio 298). The two outer and the two inner leaves in each quire are parchment, the rest is paper.
                           
                           
                           
                           Folios 299-322 contain 2 quires of 8 leaves each, 1 quires of 6 leaves, and a folding of 2 leaves at the end. All the leaves are paper.
                        
                        
                        
                        </p>
